<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>WSNH - FORMULAIRE RECRUTEUR</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="icon" sizes="16x16" type="image/png" href="https://th.bing.com/th/id/R.b10e96c930666f016df733b3d0708384?rik=8mEriFTINweOgQ&riu=http%3a%2f%2fwww.pngplay.com%2fwp-content%2fuploads%2f1%2fLetter-W-PNG-Stock-Photo.png&ehk=TaMIw3MiRv29LoFRD1wBx0E8Bgzb7lQI9PxejqN%2bDMk%3d&risl=&pid=ImgRaw&r=0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="p-5 bg-color text-white text-center">
            <h1>WORK SMARTER/</h1>
            <p>NOT HARDER</p> 
        </div>
    </header>

<main>
    <nav class="sticky-top navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-dark navbar-dark">
        <div class="container-fluid">
        <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link active" href="./">Accueil</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="fluid-container red-pannel border-top-0 border-bottom-0">
        <div class="container space">
            <h2 class="text-center fw-light">Devenir recruteur</h2>
            <p class="text-center form-text text-muted">Veuillez renseigner l'organisation dont vous faites parti pour obtenir le statut recruteur <br> Vous ne trouvez pas votre organisation ? <a class="text-center text-muted" href="/candidat/ajout_organisation">Ajoutez la !</a></p>
            <form  action="/candidat/recruiter_request" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="exampleInputEmail1">Nom de l'organisation</label>
                    <br>
                    <select id="select_organisation" name="organisation"></select>
                    <br>
                    <small id="organisationHelp" class="form-text text-muted">Votre demande sera prise en charge par un des adminisatrateurs du site.</small>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Ajouter</button>
          </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
<footer>
    <div class="p-4 bg-dark text-white text-center">
        <p>SR10 - Oriane LANFRANCHI & William SCHENTEN</p>
    </div>
</footer>
<script>
    fetch('/candidat/recruiter_form/organisations').then(res => res.json()).then(data => {
    var select = document.getElementById("select_organisation");
    for (var i = 0; i < data.length; i++) {
        var option = document.createElement("option");
        option.value = data[i].nom;
        option.text = data[i].nom;
        select.add(option);
    }
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>